---
title: Penne in Beef and Pork Red Sauce with Parmesan Cheese
description: This sauce is so much more than just a simple tomato base. It also has three hidden veggies hidden for those hard-to-please eaters in your family! The best part is they won't even notice those secret veggies thanks to this lip-smacking sauce.
